block content
  h1= title
  .content-section.parallax-section.hero-section.hidden-section(data-scrollax-parent='true')
    .bg.par-elem(data-bg='images/bg/6.jpg' data-scrollax="properties: { translateY: '30%' }")
    .overlay
    .container
        .section-title
          h4 Enjoy your time in our Hotel with pleasure.
          h2 How to Book a Room online
        .section-separator
            span
            i.fa-thin.fa-gem
    .hero-section-scroll
        .mousey
        .scroller
    .dec-corner.dc_lb
    .dec-corner.dc_rb
    .dec-corner.dc_rt
    .dec-corner.dc_lt
  .content
  .breadcrumbs-wrap
    .container
      a(href='#') Home
      a(href='#') Pages
      span Rooms And Suites
  .content-section
    .section-dec
    .content-dec2.fs-wrapper
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-8
          .post-container
            .dec-container
              .text-block
                .blog-media
                  .single-slider-wrap
                    .single-slider
                      .swiper-container
                        .swiper-wrapper.lightgallery
                          .swiper-slide.hov_zoom
                            img(src='images/all/2.jpg' alt='')
                            a.box-media-zoom.popup-image(href='images/all/2.jpg')
                              i.fal.fa-search
                          .swiper-slide.hov_zoom
                            img(src='images/all/1.jpg' alt='')
                            a.box-media-zoom.popup-image(href='images/all/1.jpg')
                              i.fal.fa-search
                          .swiper-slide.hov_zoom
                            img(src='images/all/3.jpg' alt='')
                            a.box-media-zoom.popup-image(href='images/all/3.jpg')
                              i.fal.fa-search
                    .fw-carousel-button-prev.slider-button
                      i.fa-solid.fa-caret-left
                    .fw-carousel-button-next.slider-button
                      i.fa-solid.fa-caret-right
                    .sc-controls.fwc_pag
                      .ss-slider-pagination
                .text-block.post-single_tb
                  .text-block-container
                    .tbc_subtitle Where Comfort Meets Style
                    .room-card-details(style='margin-bottom: 20px')
                      ul
                        li
                          i.fa-light.fa-calendar-days
                          span August 10, 2023
                        li
                          i.fa-light.fa-comment
                          span 2 comments
                    p.has-drop-cap
                      | Welcome to our hotel, where each room is designed to provide you with a serene and picturesque retreat. Perfect for relaxation and rejuvenation, our rooms offer stunning views of the valley, creating a tranquil atmosphere for your stay.
                      | Living Room: &quot;Experience comfort and elegance with ample seating, tastefully decorated interiors, and panoramic valley views. A perfect spot for relaxation and gathering.&quot;
                      | Bedroom: &quot;Your personal sanctuary with plush bedding, clean and cozy decor, and large windows overlooking the serene valley. Wake up to breathtaking views every morning.&quot;
                    p
                      | Each room in our hotel is meticulously maintained to ensure the highest standards of cleanliness and comfort. Our attention to detail and commitment to providing a beautiful, serene environment will make your stay truly memorable. Enjoy the seamless blend of modern amenities and natural beauty in every corner of your room.
                    .post-img-row
                      .post-img-row_item
                        img.respimg(src='images/all/5.jpg' alt='')
                      .post-img-row_item
                        img.respimg(src='images/all/6.jpg' alt='')
                  .tbc-separator
                  .tagcloud.tc_single
                    span.tc_single_title Post Tags:
                    a(href='#') Lifystyle
                    a(href='#') Travel
                    a(href='#') Trip
                    a(href='#') Outdoor
            .content-nav-fixed.dark-bg.scale_anim
              ul
                li
                  a.ln(href='/blog-single')
                    i.fal.fa-long-arrow-left
                    span
                      | Prev 
